    <div class="interview-speaker SolarisFox">
        <img src="/player/issue8/fox.png" alt="fox" />
            <div>
                <p>I was a fan of Pok&eacute;mon artwork and was curious to see if Showdown had any cool artists. c:</p>
            </div>
        </div>

    <div class="interview-speaker Faxxifer">
        <img src="/player/issue8/faxx.png" alt="faxx" />
            <div>
                <p>Ooh, very nice! As time has passed with the room, how much has it changed/grown?</p>
            </div>
        </div>

    <div class="interview-speaker SolarisFox">
        <img src="/player/issue8/fox.png" alt="fox" />
            <div>
                <p>I think the room has grown a lot. When I first joined the room, it felt mostly like just a place to hang out, but now, in addition to that we have a bit more structured activities that give our users something to talk about. I feel the room has mellowed out as well, and would not be surprised if it is currently one of the friendliest, most inviting rooms on Showdown.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

    <div class="interview-speaker Faxxifer">
        <img src="/player/issue8/faxx.png" alt="faxx" />
            <div>
