</div>

<p>In short, the Writing room offers a very new, user-friendly experience. Writers of all levels are welcome in the room; in fact, the only thing you need to do to get involved is to message one of the room Owners, who will then make a folder for you in the Cloud Drive! The room isn't solely limited to creative writing, either. If you have any interest in the aspects of writing, whether it be writing articles for pay, crafting poems for fun, or just reading the works of others for enjoyment, the Writing room is open for you.</p>

